Don’t typecast the canvas- An actor is meant to be painted in many shades.
Sometimes people tend to imagine you in a certain kind of role or look. But as an actor, it’s important to keep evolving—experimenting, surprising, and breaking the mold. Every new look is a reminder that I can be seen differently… I can look this way too.😍
